{{可再生能源}}
[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]是世界領先的[[可再生能源|可再生能源]]發電國家，發電量是排名第二的美國的兩倍多。中國可再生能源領域的增長速度超过其[[化石燃料|化石燃料]]和[[核电|核电]]能力，貢獻了全球可再生能源產能增長的43%。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web |url=https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3161732/china-remain-renewable-energy-leader-strong-capacity-growth |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-04-10 |archive-date=2022-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220520082442/https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3161732/china-remain-renewable-energy-leader-strong-capacity-growth }}</ref>2015年中国成为世界上最大的光伏发电生产国，装机容量为43GW<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/china-solar-idUSL3N15533U|title=China's solar capacity overtakes Germany in 2015, industry data show|date=21 January 2016|author=Reuters Editorial|work=Reuters|accessdate=2016-11-08|archive-date=2018-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180129021629/https://www.reuters.com/article/china-solar-idUSL3N15533U|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中国还领导世界生产和使用[[风能|风能]]和[[智能电网|智能电网]]技术，生产的水电，风能和[[太阳能|太阳能]]几乎等于法国的和德国的发电厂发电的总和。<ref>{{cite web|title=Chinese solar capacity outshone Germany's in 2015|url=http://www.businessgreen.com/bg/news/2442764/chinese-solar-capacity-outshone-germanys-in-2015|accessdate=2016-11-08|work=http://www.businessgreen.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181109150951/https://www.businessgreen.com/bg/news/2442764/chinese-solar-capacity-outshone-germanys-in-2015|archive-date=2018-11-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年中國可再生能源總裝機容量超過1000GW，佔全國總發電量的43.5%，比2015年提高10.2個百分點。中國的目標是到2060年實現80%的能源結構來自非化石能源，以及到2030年在太陽能和風能總裝機容量上達到1200GW。<ref name="#1"/>

虽然中国拥有世界上最大的太阳能和风力发电装置，但因能源需求極大及持續增長，以至在2019年中國的可再生能源只提供了所需的26%發電量，<ref>{{Cite web|title=2019 electricity & other energy statistics (preliminary)|url=https://chinaenergyportal.org/2019-electricity-other-energy-statistics-preliminary/|access-date=2021-01-06|date=2020-01-21|website=China Energy Portal {{!}} 中国能源门户|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211122222742/https://chinaenergyportal.org/2019-electricity-other-energy-statistics-preliminary/}}</ref>雖然比起2013年的20%已有明顯的進步，但目前為止大部分能源供應都仍然是由传统煤电设施提供。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=IEA - Report|url=http://www.iea.org/statistics/statisticssearch/report/?country=China&product=electricityandheat|access-date=2017-11-12|website=www.iea.org|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015004751/http://www.iea.org/statistics/statisticssearch/report/?country=China&product=electricityandheat|archive-date=2017-10-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>儘管如此，近年來可再生能源在能源結構中的比重明顯逐漸上升。2020年，可再生能源約佔中國電力新總裝機容量的40%。另外中國已承諾在2060年前實現碳中和，並在2030年前達到排放峰值。

另外，中國也將可再生能源的發展視為自身能源安全的重要戰略目標。<ref>Deng, Haifeng and Farah, Paolo Davide and Wang, Anna, China's Role and Contribution in the Global Governance of Climate Change: Institutional Adjustments for Carbon Tax Introduction, Collection and Management in China (24 November 2015). Journal of World Energy Law and Business, Oxford University Press, Volume 8, Issue 6, December 2015. Available at SSRN: http://ssrn.com/abstract=2695612</ref>中國國務院於2013年9月發布了《中國大氣污染防治行動計劃》，表明希望增加可再生能源在中國能源結構中的份額。<ref name=":02">{{Cite journal|title=China's Energy Policymaking Processes and Their Consequences|url=http://www.nbr.org/publications/issue.aspx?id=309|first1=Philip|date=November 2014|journal=The National Bureau of Asian Research Energy Security Report|last1=Andrews-Speed|access-date=5 December 2014|archive-date=2018-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806070453/http://nbr.org/publications/issue.aspx?id=309}}</ref>這是因為與容易受到地緣政治緊張局勢影響而且供應有限的石油、煤炭和天然氣不同，可再生能源系統可以在有足夠水、風和陽光的地方建造和使用，確保能源自給。<ref name="chinaen2">{{cite journal|title=Economics: Manufacture renewables to build energy security|author=John A. Mathews & Hao Tan|url=http://www.nature.com/news/economics-manufacture-renewables-to-build-energy-security-1.15847|date=10 September 2014|journal=Nature|issue=7517|doi=10.1038/513166a|volume=513|pages=166–168|bibcode=2014Natur.513..166M|pmid=25209783|s2cid=4459313|access-date=2016-11-14|archive-date=2019-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112154405/http://www.nature.com/news/economics-manufacture-renewables-to-build-energy-security-1.15847}}</ref>

隨著中國可再生能源製造業的快速發展，全球可再生能源技術的成本已大幅下降。虽然创新有所帮助，但降低成本的主要驱动因素是市场扩张。<ref name="chinaen4">{{cite journal|title=Economics: Manufacture renewables to build energy security|author=John A. Mathews & Hao Tan|url=http://www.nature.com/news/economics-manufacture-renewables-to-build-energy-security-1.15847|date=10 September 2014|journal=Nature|issue=7517|doi=10.1038/513166a|volume=513|pages=166–168|bibcode=2014Natur.513..166M|pmid=25209783|s2cid=4459313|access-date=2016-11-14|archive-date=2019-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112154405/http://www.nature.com/news/economics-manufacture-renewables-to-build-energy-security-1.15847}}</ref>2015年，中國成為全球最大的光伏發電生產國，總裝機容量為43GW。<ref>{{cite web|title=China's solar capacity overtakes Germany in 2015, industry data show|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/china-solar-idUSL3N15533U|author=Reuters Editorial|date=21 January 2016|work=Reuters|access-date=2020-12-12|archive-date=2019-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190708045939/https://www.reuters.com/article/china-solar-idUSL3N15533U}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Chinese solar capacity outshone Germany's in 2015|url=http://www.businessgreen.com/bg/news/2442764/chinese-solar-capacity-outshone-germanys-in-2015|date=21 January 2016|work=businessgreen.com|access-date=2016-11-08|archive-date=2018-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181109150951/https://www.businessgreen.com/bg/news/2442764/chinese-solar-capacity-outshone-germanys-in-2015}}</ref>從2005年到2014年，中國太陽能電池的產量增長了100倍。<ref name="chinaen3">{{cite journal|title=Economics: Manufacture renewables to build energy security|author=John A. Mathews & Hao Tan|url=http://www.nature.com/news/economics-manufacture-renewables-to-build-energy-security-1.15847|date=10 September 2014|journal=Nature|issue=7517|doi=10.1038/513166a|volume=513|pages=166–168|bibcode=2014Natur.513..166M|pmid=25209783|s2cid=4459313|access-date=2016-11-14|archive-date=2019-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112154405/http://www.nature.com/news/economics-manufacture-renewables-to-build-energy-security-1.15847}}</ref>預計到2022年實現可再生能源比化石燃料更便宜。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://qz.com/1283299/in-the-race-to-build-massive-solar-power-projects-india-is-poised-to-beat-china/|title=India is beating China in the race to build massive solar power projects|last1=N|first1=Sushma U|work=Quartz|access-date=22 May 2018|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726012024/https://qz.com/1283299/in-the-race-to-build-massive-solar-power-projects-india-is-poised-to-beat-china/}}</ref>

2017年全球可再生能源投資2798億美元，其中中國佔了全球投資的45%。<ref>Frankfurt School – UNEP Collaborating Centre for Climate & Sustainable Energy Finance (2018). ''Global Trends in Renewable Energy Investment 2018''. Available online at: https://europa.eu/capacity4dev/unep/documents/global-trends-renewable-energy-investment-2018 {{Wayback|url=https://europa.eu/capacity4dev/unep/documents/global-trends-renewable-energy-investment-2018 |date=20190408170642 }}</ref>中國已成為全球最大的可再生能源投資國、生產國和消費國。同時也是製造最先進的太陽能電池板、風力渦輪機和水力發電設施的國家，並成為世界上最大的電動汽車和電動公共汽車的生產國。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Commentary: China will bet big on clean energy to achieve carbon neutrality|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/commentary/china-climate-change-emissions-carbon-clean-energy-13533228|access-date=2022-04-10|archive-date=2021-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711170116/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/commentary/china-climate-change-emissions-carbon-clean-energy-13533228}}</ref>

