截至2019年底，該國可再生能源總裝機容量為790GW，主要來自水電、太陽能和風能，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Renewables – Global Energy Review 2020 – Analysis|url=https://www.iea.org/reports/global-energy-review-2020/renewables|access-date=2021-01-06|website=IEA|language=en-GB|archive-date=2022-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220421030758/https://www.iea.org/reports/global-energy-review-2020/renewables}}</ref>水電裝機容量達到356GW。<ref>{{Cite web|title=International Hydropower Association. Country Profile - China|url=https://www.hydropower.org/country-profiles/china|access-date=|date=|last=|first=|website=International Hydropower Association - IHA|archive-url=https://archive.today/20210106031913/https://www.hydropower.org/country-profiles/china|archive-date=6 January 2021|url-status=live}}</ref>

